message:
Hi iv got 820-00165 board 2016 it was dead liquid damaged powers on every thing is working. But fan is sping fast & running slow anyone got the asd software for this so I can run a test on please.

cheers in advance

What would you suggest start checking all the sensor any other hardware test to run on it.

cheers for the file I fixed 820-3437. ?

I recommend to inspect the areas affected by liquid first.
A simple software like Macs Fan Speed can tell you some temperature values.
You can also measure output voltage from the sensors, pages 41 & 42.
HWMonitor can help as well to tell you which sensor is failing.
Cheers guys  I will jump on that
Make sure you're using a known-good DC-In board, flex cable, trackpad, and trackpad cable. Any of these could, and usually does, cause this.
